---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import "../styles/global.css"
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contact - Suge & Company | Advocate</title>
</head>
<Layout>
  <body class="flex flex-col w-full h-full " style="background: var(--color-secondary)">
  <main class="flex-grow px-4 py-8 md:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">
      About Us
    </h1>

    <section class="mb-12 sm:mb-16 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-8 ">
      <div class="prose max-w-none flex-1  ">
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-gray-800">
          At Suge & Company, we are more than legal professionals — we are dedicated 
          partners in your pursuit of justice, resolution, and peace of mind. Founded
          on the core values of integrity, transparency, and client-focused service, 
          our firm brings together a team of experienced attorneys committed to delivering 
          strategic, personalized legal solutions.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-gray-800">
          We understand that every case is unique. Whether you're navigating a complex 
          business matter, protecting your family's interests, or seeking justice in a
          personal dispute, our approach is rooted in clear communication, rigorous preparation,
          and a deep respect for your time and trust.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-gray-800">
          With a strong reputation for results and a passion for advocacy, we take pride 
          in standing by our clients through every step of their legal journey. At Suge & 
          Company, you're not just another case — you're a valued client, and your goals are our mission.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex-1 w-full relative h-[300px] sm:h-[400px] lg:h-[500px] rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-[url('../assets/images/about.jpeg')] bg-cover bg-center opacity-90">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-30 dark:bg-opacity-50"></div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold p-4 sm:p-8 relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center text-white">
          Welcome To<br>
          <span class="text-yellow-300">Suge and Company</span><br>
          <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl">Advocate</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 sm:p-8 rounded-xl">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
        Our Core Values
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">
            Integrity
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            We uphold the highest ethical standards in all our dealings.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">
            Transparency
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Clear communication and honesty in every client relationship.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">
            Client Focus
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Your needs and goals are at the center of everything we do.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  </body>
</Layout>
</html>

<style is:global>
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .dark .bg-cover::after {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }
  
  /* Prose content in dark mode */
  .dark .prose {
    color: var(--color-gray-300);
  }
  
  .dark .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-gray-100);
  }
</style>